data.description: Discover your sanctuary at 16255 Valley Bottom Rd in scenic Sutter Creek, California. Embrace a life of tranquility in this meticulously maintained home that offers remarkable features and breathtaking views. With three bedrooms and three bathrooms spanning 2,262 square feet, the open floor plan seamlessly blends living, dining, and kitchen spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation. Beyond the home lies the charming community of Sutter Creek, known for its small-town allure, friendly neighbors, and vibrant atmosphere. Seize the opportunity to call this home yours!
